  <description type="morphology">Stems reddish, short glandular-pubescent, viscid. Leaves: petiole 1–4.5 cm; blade
        ovate to elliptic, 2.5–7 × 1–3 cm, margins entire to sinuate, sparsely short scabrous;
        surfaces glandular-pubescent, ± viscid, adaxial surface green or slightly glaucous.
        Inflorescences 10–30-flowered; bracts green, ovate to lanceolate, 3–12 × 1.5–3.5 mm, base
        attenuate, margins glandular short ciliate, viscid-pubescent. Perianth: tube greenish to
        pink, 8–25 mm, limb bright magenta, 10–15 mm diam., lobes well developed. Fruits oval to ±
        round in profile, 7–13 × 8–17 mm, walls indurate, transversely rugose or ribbed; lateral
        ribs prominent, extending into wings; wings 2(–3).</description>
